			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">New UI: &quot;With Bards In Mind&quot;<a name="65458"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 3 04 8:05 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>As the title suggests this 1280x1024 UI was designed to make my Bard's life a little easier, although it may also be suitable for hybrid/caster/pet classes. 
<br />

<br />
Inventory slots in the Pet window have been arranged to flank the container mod provided. This makes item switching/right clicking very easy and does away with the need to use large, cumbersome inventory/container combo mods. Hint: you can position multiple bags at the same spot if you need to swap out items in other bags. 
<br />

<br />
Note: OoW compatible 9 slot spell bar included (9th gem does not show up in screenshots because I don't have the AA yet <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> )
<br />

<br />

<br />
Hopefully available for d/l on eqinterface.com in the near future.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
<img src="http://img72.exs.cx/img72/6080/bagopen1.jpg"></span></td>
